    <item>
      <title>由于利率不确定性激增，抵押贷款债券表现落后于国债</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/mortgage-bonds-lag-treasuries-as-uncertainty-about-rates-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者准备迎接可能的降息，从而带来更多房主再融资，利率走向的不确定性日益增加，导致机构抵押贷款债券周一的表现差于美国国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/mortgage-bonds-lag-treasuries-as-uncertainty-about-rates-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 18:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
